Governor Godwin Obaseki of the Peoples Democratic Party is currently leading in the Edo governorship election. Obaseki, who is seeking a second term in office as governor, is leading his main opponent, Osagie Ize-Iyamu of the All Progressives Congress. Godwin Obaseki Results from 14 local government areas announced by the Independent National Electoral Commission so far indicate that Obaseki polled a total of 254,169 while Ize-Iyamu had a total of 163,429 votes. See Also






